org.silex.runtime.ressource.LoadingTypeValue

defined in
org.silex.runtime.ressource.RessourceData
Enumerates the file type which can be loaded : data for text file, image for picture such as .jpg, .gif and .png files, text for html text files, animation for animated format such as .swf and .svg, container for skin loading (.swf, .html), and library for classes library which may be stored in .swf or .js files for instance
